+to the NULL:
+[    0.157054] missing gpiochip .dev parent pointer
+[    0.157287] bcma: bus0: Error registering GPIO driver: -22
+introduced by the commit 74f4e0cc6108 ("bcma: switch GPIO portions to
+use GPIOLIB_IRQCHIP").
